languages.text: "Вы бы не справились лучше, префект — сколько бы не мнили себя спасительницей протектората, которой вы сами себя назначили!"
"You couldn't have done any better, Prefect, no matter how fervently you believe yourself to be the saviour of the protectorate — an appointment you bestowed upon yourself!"

languages.text: « Vous n'auriez pas pu faire mieux, préfète, malgré votre conviction inébranlable d'être la gardienne du protectorat – un rôle que vous vous êtes attribué vous-même. »

languages.text: “就算换做是你，也没办法做得更好，行政官。或许你满脑子以为你自己才是这个王朝的救世主，但那不过是你一厢情愿的僭越而已！”
languages.original_text: "You couldn't have done any better, Prefect, no matter how fervently you believe yourself to be the saviour of the protectorate — an appointment you bestowed upon yourself!"

languages.text: «Usted no podría haberlo hecho mejor, prefecta, por más convencida que esté de ser la salvadora del protectorado, ¡título que se adjudica usted misma!».
languages.original_text: "You couldn't have done any better, Prefect, no matter how fervently you believe yourself to be the saviour of the protectorate — an appointment you bestowed upon yourself!"

languages.text: 「総監、自分が保護領の救世主だと、どれほど熱心に信じていようと、これ以上のことはできなかっただろう。その『救世主』という役割は、君自身が勝手に与えたものだがな！」
languages.original_text: "You couldn't have done any better, Prefect, no matter how fervently you believe yourself to be the saviour of the protectorate — an appointment you bestowed upon yourself!"

languages.text: "Bıraksak daha iyi karar mı alacaktın Prefekt? Kendini protektoranın kurtarıcısı sanıyorsun... O işler öyle olmuyor!"
